    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Handle 'job.start' → Notion\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Consolidate Handling · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
